PrecisEnactment of an ORDER AUTHORIZING FEDERAL EMPLOYEES TO ACQUIRE INTERESTS IN CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (ORDER NO.3, 1999) - which authorizes Wayne Angus Keefe, of the Town of Hay River, N.W.T., to lease some 0.54 hectares of un-surveyed land situated near the 36th kilometre of Highway No. 1, in the Northwest Territories, for recreational purposes.
